OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FThe search for new accommodation for
OL,7,Fasylum seekers has been put on hold in
OL,8,Fthe North East as the government deems
OL,9,Fthe area to have reached capacity.
OL,11,FThe Home Office is continuing to look
OL,12,Ffor housing elsewhere in the country
OL,13,Fbut has put the pause in the region
OL,14,Fdown to having what it believes to be
OL,15,Fsufficient capacity.
OL,17,FIt follows two consecutive weekends of
OL,18,Fprotests in the North East, which is
OL,19,Fhome to a higher than average number
OL,20,Fof people seeking asylum per head in
OL,21,Fthe UK.
