OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FThe latest protest by anti-immigration
OL,7,Fcampaigners took place in Newcastle
OL,8,Fcity centre on Saturday (9 August).
OL,10,FBini Araia, project manager at refugee
OL,11,Fcharity Investing in People and
OL,12,FCulture on Teesside, said he believed
OL,13,Fmore people have been accommodated in
OL,14,Fthe region as a result of cheaper and
OL,15,Fmore available housing.
OL,17,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees he did not want
OL,18,Fto comment on government policy itself
OL,19,Fbut said fewer asylum seekers would
OL,20,Fmean fewer people contributing to the
OL,21,FNorth East economy and communities.
