OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,F"By limiting the numbers coming into
OL,7,Fthe North East, eventually we are
OL,8,Flimiting the number of benefits we can
OL,9,Fget after people are given permission
OL,10,Fto work, are given refugee status and
OL,11,Fare contributing to the economy."
OL,13,FMr Araia lives and works in
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough which, according to Home
OL,15,FOffice figures, has the seventh
OL,16,Fhighest number of asylum seekers per
OL,17,F10,000 people.
