OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FHe said that individual asylum seekers
OL,7,Fultimately have no choice of where
OL,8,Fthey are housed, adding: "That is not
OL,9,Fusually understood by some people in
OL,10,Fthe community and I think I would like
OL,11,Fto make the point that asylum seekers
OL,12,Fare desperate to work, they want to
OL,13,Fwork."
OL,15,FAccording to the Home Office, as of
OL,16,FJune 2024, the total 'work in
OL,17,Fprogress' asylum caseload consisted of
OL,18,F224,700 cases.
