OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FOf these, around 88,000 cases were
OL,7,Fawaiting an initial decision and
OL,8,F138,000 cases had received an initial
OL,9,Frefusal and were awaiting some kind of
OL,10,Ffurther action.
OL,12,FThe total asylum caseload has
OL,13,Fquadrupled in size since 2014, driven
OL,14,Fboth by applicants waiting longer for
OL,15,Fan initial decision and a growth in
OL,16,Fthe number of people subject to
OL,17,Fremoval action following a negative
OL,18,Fdecision.
