OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FThere were more than 400 asylum hotels
OL,7,Fin use across the UK in Autumn 2023 at
OL,8,Fa cost of almost #9 million per day.
OL,10,FIn the months before the election, the
OL,11,Fasylum backlog soared again, according
OL,12,Fto the government, leaving the asylum
OL,13,Fsystem under unprecedented strain.
OL,15,FOn Saturday 2 August, four people were
OL,16,Farrested in connection with alleged
OL,17,Fpublic order offences during a protest
OL,18,Fin Newcastle.
