OL,3,CSearch for asylum seeker housing in
OL,4,CNorth East on hold
OL,6,FAbout 200 anti-immigration
OL,7,Fcampaigners, and an opposing group of
OL,8,Fanti-fascist demonstrators, gathered
OL,9,Fnear a hotel said to be housing asylum
OL,10,Fseekers.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police described the
OL,13,Farrests as "disappointing", saying the
OL,14,Fprotests mainly passed without
OL,15,Fincident.
